    <item>
      <title>纽森在打击无家可归者后继续严厉打击犯罪</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-16/newsom-extends-get-tough-push-to-crime-after-homeless-crackdown</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加州州长加文·纽瑟姆签署了一系列反犯罪法案，表明在呼吁严厉打击无家可归者营地三周后，加州将对零售盗窃和汽车盗窃采取更严厉的手段。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-16/newsom-extends-get-tough-push-to-crime-after-homeless-crackdown</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 16 Aug 2024 20:58:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
